---
title: Grilled Chicken & Cheesy Charred Broccoli Salad with Honey Mustard Mayonnaise
description: Turn up the heat with tonight’s chicken feast, fresh off the barbecue! The charred broccoli salad has won our hearts (and our stomachs) - tender and smokey, and tossed with a garlic chilli butter, it’s the star of the show! Drizzle over a sweet and tangy honey mustard mayo, and this flavourful combo is the perfect way to bring that backyard barbecue vibe to your plate.
